\subsection{Existing Models: Additive DLNMs}
\label{ss:existingDLNM}
The ACE-DLNM and DRF-DLNM make different assumptions about lagged effects of a time-varying exposure, and both have been extended to incorporate additive effects of multiple exposures \citep{pan2025estimating,gasparrini2017penalized}.

